Essence All About Chocolates Eyeshadow Review, Swatches, EOTD Hello my favourite people,
I am a total makeup junkie and like trying new stuff to create various makeup looks, but there is one area where I have to learn a lot and that is – eye makeup. I am very amateur at eye makeup. But when I saw these cute little palettes, I was tempted to explore this section. I got a very starters kind of a kit to experiment with first and then I will review some larger palettes. For now, here I present “All About Chocolates”!

Price:
Rs 399
Product Description:
All about… beautiful eyes: a gorgeous look is guaranteed by the eye-shadow palettes with six trendy colours each. The smooth texture of the eye-shadows contains shimmering, matt and metallic effects – for endless looks.
My Experience with Essence All About Chocolates Eyeshadow:

I was really tempted to pick this palette because it looked very neutral to me and would be my on-the-go palette. The palette is very small and handy. I love how cute it looks! It actually looks like a beginner’s palette, very sweet and simple. It comes in a plastic pan and I can easily see the shades from outside. The pricing is also very reasonable since they are offering an entire palette at that cost which is a good deal for beginners and college goers. Coming to the shades, they looked very different when I tried at the counter on my hand. Also the name “All about chocolates” doesn’t seem very apt because the colours are not as chocolaty.

Three shades are metallic browns, one is a warm copper metallic brown and the other two more of beiges and whites which would actually do a job of a highlighter. When I actually tried doing the smokey eyes look, I was surprised! The shades did not appear different from one another. They looked pretty much the same and very close to each other. I blended them to create a simple eye makeup look but only the darkest shade of the palette looked a little different. Hence, my eye makeup became very restricted. But the colours are really great for a simple festive look or just to add a little more spice to the simple everyday eye makeup.

The shades contain a bit of shimmer but these shimmer particles altogether form a metallic base which looks glamorous and stunning. The shades cause a minimal fallout but may irritate the eyes if a lot of product enters the eyes. It went in my eyes and irritated a lot for some minutes and plus I am a contact lens wearer, so imagine how difficult that situation would have been for me. It added a dose of redness to my eyes which settles down after 20-25 minutes; either my eyes are too sensitive or the formula has some issue.

The addition of the highlighter shades to the makeup look makes a lot of difference. It enhances the eye area so much and the eyes look wide open by highlighting the inner corners, but the highlighting of inner corners vanishes in just an hour while the highlighting on the brow bone stays long. The shadows stay for 5-6 hours on my eyes as it is and even more with a primer. So overall, I think it is a nice, decent palette for beginners. But if you are more into eye makeup and know various tricks, then you will end up not liking this one because there are so many better palettes than this one.



Pros of Essence All About Chocolates Eyeshadow:
• Very sweet and simple palette for beginners and college-goers
• Very reasonably priced and a lot of variants to choose from
• “All About Chocolates” is a very neutral palette and it can be used daily as well occasionally
• The shades have a metallic base which looks absolutely gorgeous and classy on the eyes
• The texture is very smooth and glides easily on the eyelids without a lot of fallout
• The highlighter works very well and defines the brow bone brilliantly
• The eyeshadow stays on my eyes for 5-6 hours without a primer
Cons of Essence All About Chocolates Eyeshadow:
• On my hand, the shades look different but on the eyes they all look the same or say very close
• All the shades blend with each other making only one shade noticeable on my eyes
• The name isn’t very apt because they are not chocolate browns; they are more of grey, brown and beige
• The palette looked like it has the potential to create smokey eyes because the shades were available from light to dark, but it failed totally
• The little fallout caused a lot of redness in my eyes and irritated my eyes for long
Will I Repurchase/Recommend Essence All About Chocolates Eyeshadow?
I recommend it if you are starting to explore the eye makeup field but I have seen a lot of better palettes than this. I would buy palettes with more variety of shades rather than something like this.
IMBB Rating:
3.5/5
Conclusion:
Essence is one of the best drugstore brands to try if you like using makeup regularly with poppy and vibrant shades.

KAOS is a SUPERCHARGER? 3 Dark Edition Starter Packs for Skylanders Superchargers w/ GAMEPLAY! REACT This is the first year there will be 3 different Dark Starter Packs for the same Skylanders game!  Kaos is not a supercharger by the way, but the Dark Kaos Trophy somehow adds to the story and I'm sure we'll learn more soon.  The Doom Jet is another Vehicle for Kaos on top of the Ultimate Doomstation of Destruction.

►Sky Kids react to Skylanders Superchargers Eon's Elite: 

Who's Dark this time around?
SUPERCHARGERS:
Dark Supershot Stealth Elf
Dark Hammer Slam Bowser
Dark Turbo Charge Donkey Kong
Dark Spitfire
VEHICLES:
Dark Sea Shadow
Dark Hot Streak
Dark Clown Cruiser
Dark Barrel Blaster

All Dark Edition Starter Packs will be available for a suggested retail price of $99.99 and include Dark Spitfire, Dark Hot Streak, a two-sided ultimate collector poster and the highly sought-after Kaos Trophy, which is the only way to unlock special Kaos gameplay content. 
Dark Super Shot Stealth Elf and Dark Sea Shadow will be available exclusively in the Dark Edition Starter Packs for Xbox One, Xbox 360, PlayStation® 3 and PlayStation® 4. The Wii U™ Dark Edition Starter Pack will include Dark Turbo Charge Donkey Kong and Dark Barrel Blaster, exclusively. A different, unique adventure including Dark Hammer Slam Bowser and Dark Clown Cruiser will be made available on Nintendo's Wii™ system.  The WII starter pack box says RACING, and is a completely different experience.

• 1 plastic straw

Vegas Haul | Beauty, Fashion, and Music Note to self: Bring a second suitcase the next time I go on vacation.
The tricky thing about shopping while traveling is making sure you'll have the space in your carryon bag for all of the new stuff. I purchased quite a few things while in Vegas, but most of the items are smaller so I was able to group them and decrease the amount of photos needed for this already long post. I purchased a few beauty, fashion, and music items, so let's jump right in with beauty products first.

From MAC

Plum lipliner
Whirl lipstick - matte finish
Verve lipstick - satin finish
Evening Rendezvous - matte finish

Almost immediately after I shared my favorite Mac lipsticks, Whirl and the lipliner I pair with it (Plum) disappeared. I have no idea where I misplaced them, but after many failed attempts to locate the dynamic duo, I accepted the fact that I'd have to repurchase. I'm still low key hoping I can find them, because that'll mean I'll have two tubes of one of my favorite lipstick shades. Anyways, I went into MAC purely to repurchase those two items. I also picked up Verve because the shade looked like it would be a pretty brown once applied. Breaking out of the neutral shell, the last shade I picked up was Evening Rendezvous. I've had a few purple shades in my day, but what I like about this one is the lack of vibrancy. The purple tone is soft enough against my lips to not be the focal point if that makes sense. The only thing that throws me off is the packaging. Although beautiful (it's from the Magic of the Night collection), I like to keep the packaging consistent with my MAC lipsticks since they're on display.
 From Sephora

Glamglow SuperMud Clearing Treatment
Glamglow Youthmud Tinglexfoliate Treatment
Anastasia Beverly Hills Brow Wiz in Chocolate
Kat Von D Limited Edition Lolita Lip Duo
Buxom Objects of Obsession 500 Point Perk Box

I've wanted to try the Glamglow products for a while now, and the VIB sale was the perfect time to indulge. I'm seriously hoping I like them, especially because I'm still on the hunt for a good skincare routine. Although there are gift sets now that are a pretty good deal, I don't have any interest in what they're offering. I've only wanted to try the white and black glamglow masks, so I purchased the full-size Supermud mask and travel size Youthmud mask. I haven't tried either out just yet, but I'll share my experience once I do.

Those were my splurge purchases, but I also picked up another Brow Wiz for when the ones I have inevitably run out. A spur of the moment purchase of course had to happen as I was walking through the checkout. I quickly swatched the Kat Von D Lolita duo and headed to the cashier. By the time I was ready to pay, I looked down at my hand and really liked the color of Lolita once it dried. Lolita II was a little lackluster, but I figured I might as well pick the duo up while it's available. I just applied Lolita as I'm writing this post, and it looks like a mixture between Whirl and Verve. I haven't tried out Lolita II yet, but it looks like it will have a warm tint that I'm not too keen on.

Sephora has had a lot of great rewards this year, I don't think I've ever cashed in my points as much as I did during 2015. This last trip was no exception, as I redeemed 500 more points to nab the Buxom box. I've had trial sizes of the Buxom lip products previously and enjoyed them, so I figured their box would be a good choice. The cashier agreed, which makes me even more excited to try out some of the products inside.
From Nectar Bath Treats

Vanilla Rose Donut Soap
Guava Tangerine Cupcake Soap

This purchase was simply me being a tourist. We stayed at the Signature at MGM Grand, and downstairs was the cutest little boutique called Nectar Bath Treats. Nectar Bath Treats sells high quality bath products, and a majority of them are carved to look like desserts. As good as they smell, I don't plan on using them. I purchased one bar of soap that looks like a pretty sprinkled donut, and another that's in the shape of a delicate cupcake. I'm not a keychain person, so these soaps are my souvenirs.
 From Topshop

Quay 'Modern Love' Sunglasses
Orelia London Rose Gold Earrings

Surprisingly, I went to Topshop and didn't purchase a single Topshop item. I fell in love with an olive bomber jacket that had gold detailing, but the petite version felt a bit short in the sleeves. Don't you hate it when that happens? It takes me forever to find a nice coat, so when I do, I want to purchase it on sight. I did end up purchasing a pair of Quay Australia glasses. I haven't purchased a pair since my initial haul and review post from late Spring so I don't know if their packaging has changed or if in-store purchases have a different case. They look the same on the outside, but the quality of the sunglasses case is much lower than what I received when I ordered from online. Despite that, I really like my purchase. I picked up the Modern Love style in black

私は唇の色がほとんどなく、血色が悪い!
ティント系で色がしっかり残る強いものを使うと
唇の皮がポロポロ剥けてしまう
最近も、色持ちがいいティントを使って
唇が乾燥してしまい、唇周りも少しガサガサ気味(動画お見苦しくてごめんなさい)
・
シアーな感じでツヤっとしているリップはどうしても色持ちが悪い!
少しでも口紅の色持ちをよくさせる為にしている塗り方をご紹介します!
・
・
リップ下地は必ず塗ります!マット系のリップを次に重ねるときは、M・A・Cのプレッププライムリップを塗ることが多いです✨
次に塗るマット系のリップの密着感がよくなります♡
・
マット系のリップを塗ります。私がよく使うのは、
上に赤系のリップを塗るときは
CHANELルージュアリュールヴェルヴェット58✨
メインのリップを何にするかで下に塗るマットリップの色を変えています♡
ブラシはエチュードハウスのものです!
キャップがなく、スライド式なので持ち歩きにも便利
・
ティッシュでおさえます!
指で触っても色がつかない程度になるまでおさえます✨
マットリップ自体の色味は薄くなるけどOKです!
・
メインのリップを塗ります!
今回は、マキアージュ ドラマティックルージュBE777✨
これ1本でも綺麗に発色するのですが、色持ちが優れて良い訳ではないので長時間お直しが出来ないときはこの方法です!
・
薄い唇のぷっくり感を出す為に、リップアディクトを重ねます♡
アプリケーターに色が付くのが嫌なので、上から重ねるときはブラシにとって付けています✨
・
・
これで完成です✨
落ちやすいけどお気に入りというリップはこの方法でうまく色持ちさせています♡
ちなみに、上にコーラルピンク系のリップを重ねるときはベージュ系のマットリップを仕込んでいますよ✨

「重厚感がラグジュアリーの象徴になることももちろんありますが、今回の『ガブリエル』という名前に寄り添うためには、清廉さや純粋さを極めることが大切だと考えました。
そのためにはガラスはできる限り薄く、軽く仕上げなくてはならない。ボトルの開発に取り掛かったのは2009年のことです」。 シャネル社の伝説的アートディレクター、ジャック エリュの愛弟子。彼のもとで手腕を磨き、1993年よりシャネルのパッケージ・グラフィック制作責任者の役職に就くシルヴィ ルガストゥロワは、こう語ってくれました。 
ルミナスなフローラルアコードにふさわしい透明感。ボトルは、フランス製。しかし従来のように内側ではなく、外側にまろやかに押し上げた弧を磨く作業は、ボヘミアの研磨職人に託しました。 「最終の仕上げはコットンの布で磨き上げて完成させます。この研磨技術は、専門の職人が特別に訓練して、やっと得た技なんですよ」。 着想源を探して、カンボン通りのシャネルのプライベートサロンを訪れると、3つの銀のジュエリーボックスを手に、シルヴィはこうも教えてくれました。 「蓋を開けてみてください。内側がゴールドになっていますよね? ここにこそシャネルのエッセンスが凝縮されています。つまりラグジュアリーは目には見えない。美とは、外だけでなく内なるもの、ということ」。 発売になったばかりの香水「ガブリエル」。薄い、繊細なガラスに包まれた黄金の芳香は、シャネルがまた一歩、新しい時代に踏み出したことを教えてくれます。 
9月29日(金)から3日間だけ、「ガブリエル シャネル」 スペシャルイベントが開催されます。そのボトルと、香りと、マドモアゼル シャネルのエスプリに触れるチャンスです。入場無料。場所は東京ミッドタウン アトリウム(●東京都港区赤坂9-7-1)
